name: Eye Of The Tiger EP (2009)
description: EYE OF THE TIGER is DON’T DISTURB MY CIRCLES first EP freely released in July 2009, a DIY (do it yourself) record conceptualized, envisioned, created and produced solely by the band members at their home studio. It presents us with a diversified range of musical styles, in a disconcerted experimental mix of arrangements where there is simply one rebel rule: there’s no rules! As this might seem an axiomatic contradiction, a loud listening paints the real atmospheres and virtual landscapes (with freedom written all over it) that inspired the band. Featuring immortal quotations V for Vendetta and the all mighty Hercules, Arnold Schwarzenegger character from his first movie Hercules in New York 1970, EYE OF THE TIGER unleashes the beast and sets it free as free can be! Tracklist: 01 Moonwalking In Purgatory 02 We Are The Anthem 03 This Is Your Celebration Song 04 Like Clouds Decapitating Trees 05 Death Was Her Role Model In doubt? Download and listen to it for free: http://www.dontdisturbmycircles.com
